Live event tracking
Location Data
Technical and Usage Data
Identity Data
When you attend an event, we may track your location if you download our app or via your pass in a variety of ways.  For example, we may track your location if you scan your pass using one of our event scanners.  These are located throughout our venues including at exhibitor stands or the entrance/exit of our live events.  We may also be able to track you location via our beacons located our venues for example where where you are in close proximity to a stand even if you haven’t scanned your badge.  We carry out this tracking to understand what parts of the show you have visited for our own insight and analysis purposes
Consent
